imdb.plot outline: This season covers the nutritional value of an average person's daily food intake in the most fun way. It shows the careful segregation of the mineral value of every food item, coupled with interesting facts of the effect of it on other livings beings that consume it. From the natural abilities of monkeys to swing from one tree to another to lions tearing meat, food has never been more exciting.
